data.description: A Great Room with a wood burning fireplace welcomes you to this charming Glenside single. Be amazed at the condition of the original hardwood floors as you stroll thru the large Living Room and adjacent Formal Dining Room. The Kitchen features a gas stove, dishwasher and an outside doorway to the side yard. First floor also has a full size tile bath and 2 bedrooms or office space. The second floor boasts a huge master suite with plenty of storage. While the partially finished basement is ready to entertain with a stove  a  Wine Cellar and a half bath,  continue the party thru the outside entrance to a very large rear yard. This home also features a detached garage, Central Air,  extra long driveway for several cars and plenty of off street parking!  Other amenities include; Close to shopping and major highways, walking distance to train, Abington Schools, and much more! Hurry this Gem won't last!
